verbose_text: Differentially expressed circRNAs with a high fold-change were selected for validation by RT-qPCR : circRNA-003780, circRNA-010056, and circRNA-010231 were upregulated and circRNA-003424, circRNA-013630, circRNA-001489 and circRNA-018127 were downregulated (fold-change> 4, P < 0.05) in M1 compared to M2, which was found to correlate with the microarray data.
evidence: circRNA-010231 were upregulated and circRNA-003424, circRNA-013630, circRNA-001489 and circRNA-018127 were downregulated (fold-change >4, P<0.05) in M1
